
README for the CMSSW installation on cvmfs prepared by Bockjoo Kim on 02MAY2020

[1] What is CMSSW?
It is the CMS software that are used by the entire CMS collaboration for production, processing, and analysis.
CMSSW is developed and built. The release is announced and published in the release map {1}.

[2] Installation of CMSSW
Based on the release map, all announced new CMSSW releases are installed.
We use the script $HOME/run_install_cmssw.sh
However, as of April 2, 2020, the installation is handled by Jenkins {2}.


